high_descs: Turn right and walk forward, then turn left to face the kitchen counter.
Pick  up the egg to the right of the kettle.
Turn around, step forward, then turn left and walk to the counter on the far side, turn left to face the microwave.
Open the microwave, place the egg to the left of the apple and turn on. Wait till the microwave is off and remove the egg.
Turn around, walk towards the fridge, turn right and go straight till you reach the trash can on the left.
Place the egg in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Heat up an egg in the microwave and put in the trash.

high_descs: Walk ahead and turn left to face the counter on the right side of the stove.
Pick up the egg on the counter.
Heat the egg in the microwave.
Turn right and walk to the fridge, then go past it and face the bin on the right side of it.
Place the egg in the bin.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked egg in a garbage bin.

high_descs: Turn right and walk straight slightly then turn left and face the counter right of the stove
Pick up the egg next to the tea kettle
Move slightly to the right and face the microwave
Place the egg in the microwave and heat it then remove it
Turn around and walk straight then turn right at the kitchen island walk straight then face left at the trash bin
Place the egg inside the trash bin next to the refrigerator
anns.task_desc: Heat an egg and place it in the trash bin
